---
description: Enforce Larrick branch-domain ownership and branch naming.
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use `codex/<workflow>/<short-topic>` branch naming for task branches.
- Land changes on owning `dev/<workflow>` first, then promote to `main`.
- Do not propose edits outside the owning domain paths unless explicitly requested.
- Do not push directly to `main` or any `dev/*` branch.
